{"tid":424652,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[快運UO] 窮撚去日本旅行package","createTime":"2017-10-05T02:55:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T03:00:08.000Z","uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cf9d45ac8fe22f3c69da4aff152ecc492c0323b6","tid":424652,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T02:55:17.000Z","msg":"坐快運, 仲要非mega sale唔買,<br />\n黃昏時間出發, 晨咁早就回程<br />\n一定唔會買寄艙行李, 手提行李多到好似走難咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買最cheap既保險 (甚至唔買)<br />\n一出事個陣就屌鳩保險乜都唔賠<br />\n<br />\n頭尾兩晚瞓機場,<br />\n期餘日子住hostel或者膠囊酒店<br />\n<br />\n餐餐食lawson<br />\n有時夜晚食松屋, 仲扮到食家咁, 話松屋好食過吉野家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食餐拉麵好似要攞佢條命咁 (明明拉麵都係平野)<br />\n<br />\n呢種人真係好低賤,<br />\n不過再低賤啲就會係度回應: 你葡萄我呀? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1fcdb39944e959e6a1e89c926daadd58c72fad4","tid":424652,"uid":9411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T02:58:20.000Z","msg":"你葡萄我呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7cf4341a082de005f3b254946e000fecb5f4102","tid":424652,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T02:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你葡萄我呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n低賤人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ab717ae7020841756a12575f9b767bc5e8c8475","tid":424652,"uid":16061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T03:00:08.000Z","msg":"是但啦 人地搭頭等又關你事咩<br />\n顧好自己啦"}]}